1. *Naučio* sam da vozim automobil (I learned to drive a car).
2. On je *naučila* matematiku brzo (He learned math quickly).
3. Učiteljica je *naučila* decu novo pismo (The teacher taught the children a new alphabet).
4. On je *naučio* da razmišlja kritički (He learned to think critically).
5. Oni su *naučili* da pamte detalje (They learned to remember details).
6. Ona se *naučila* da pleše (She learned to dance).
7. Mi ćemo *naučiti* nova vrsta muzike (We will learn a new type of music). 
8. Oni su *naučili* da se koriste računarom (They learned to use a computer).